      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Congratulations! You have just invested your resources in the methods
    of this phase, now it is time to go ahead with development of these methods.
    The players must move forward and look at the methods and how well they are developed.
    Players must discuss amongst themselves if they are satisfied with how well the
    methods look. These methods are useful in understanding the how the different
    phases of a project are completed and give insights on how we can apply them
    to other projects in our organizations. \r\n\r\nIf they are satisfied, then you
    can move ahead to the Phase End Event, otherwise, you can re-invest in these
    methods again in the next round. This decision should be taken after discussion
    with all the colleagues. The Game Master can choose the path, in the Game UI.
    \r\n\r\nHint: It is recommended that you develop your methods well before moving
    to the phase end event as the phase end event might require information from
    these methods to complete it."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
